'''细胞谱系'''指的是一个组织或器官从[[受精|受精]][[胚胎|胚胎]]开始的发育历史<ref>{{Cite book|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/cell+lineage|title=Collins English Dictionary - Complete & Unabridged 10th Edition.|publisher=HarperCollins Publishers.|accessdate=2 June 2014}}</ref>。一個生物體內的細胞會發生[[細胞分裂|細胞分裂]]，過程持續至一个不會再分裂的成熟细胞後分裂終止。细胞谱系正是基于对细胞祖先的追踪而得出'''<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cell Identification and Cell Lineage Analysis|last=Giurumescu|first=Claudiu A.|last2=Chisholm|first2=Andrew D.|date=2011|journal=Methods in Cell Biology|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-544172-8.00012-8|volume=106|pages=325–341|isbn=9780125441728|issn=0091-679X|pmc=4410678|pmid=22118283}}</ref>'''。研究人員也可以通过标记一个细胞（用荧光分子或其他可追踪的标记）并跟踪其细胞分裂后的后代来研究细胞谱系<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Post-embryonic cell lineages of the nematode, ''Caenorhabditis elegans''|last=Sulston|first=JE|last2=Horvitz|first2=HR|journal=[[Developmental_Biology_(journal)|Developmental Biology]]|issue=1|doi=10.1016/0012-1606(77)90158-0|year=1977|volume=56|pages=110–56|pmid=838129}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The postembryonic cell lineages of the hermaphrodite and male gonads in ''Caenorhabditis elegans''|last=Kimble|first=J|last2=Hirsh|first2=D|journal=[[Developmental_Biology_(journal)|Developmental Biology]]|issue=2|doi=10.1016/0012-1606(79)90035-6|year=1979|volume=70|pages=396–417|pmid=478167}}</ref>。

